The files celeryd and celerybeat files need to go in the corresponding locations
from your root folder.

You may also need t change the paths in the celeryd and celerybeat files added
to the /etc/default/ folder to match the user you will use to run celery and also
the install location you have chosen for PYGRDT.

/etc/default/celeryd
/etc/default/celerybeat

/etc/init.d/celeryd
/etc/init.d/celerybeat


